      • createUser

        public static boolean createUser(TGServer tgServer,
                                 java.lang.String tgNetListenerName,
                                 java.lang.String user,
                                 java.lang.String pwd,
                                 java.lang.String logFile,
                                 java.lang.String logLevel,
                                 long timeout)
                          throws TGAdminException
        Create a user. Operation blocks until it is completed.
        Parameters:
        tgServer - TG server to create user from
        tgNetListenerName - Name of the net listener for TG Admin to connect to - if null connect to 1st one
        user - username to be created
        pwd - user password
        logFile - TG admin log file location - Generated by admin
        logLevel - Specify the log level: info/user1/user2/user3/debug/debugmemory/debugwire
        timeout - Number of milliseconds allowed to complete the stop server operation - If lower than 0 wait forever
        Returns:
        true if user creation succeeded
        Throws:
        TGAdminException - Admin execution fails or timeout occurs

        tgHome - TG admin home
        url - Url to connect to TG server
        user - User name
        pwd - User password
        logFile - TG admin log file location - Generated by admin
        logLevel - Specify the log level: info/user1/user2/user3/debug/debugmemory/debugwire
        waitToCompletion - Number of milliseconds to wait for this call to return
        Returns:
        Output console of stop operation
        Throws:
        TGAdminException - Admin execution fails
